{"id": "art-584", "label": "Art. 584", "title": "Art. 584: Înlocuirea pedepsei detenţiunii pe viaţă", "slug": "art-584", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1000742073\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1116\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1000742073\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 584:\nÎnlocuirea pedepsei deten&#355;iunii pe via&#355;&#259; </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1924633170\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1115\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1924633170\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Înlocuirea pedepsei deten&#355;iunii pe via&#355;&#259;\ncu pedeapsa închisorii se dispune, la cererea procurorului ori a persoanei\ncondamnate, de c&#259;tre instan&#355;a de executare, iar dac&#259; persoana\ncondamnat&#259; se afl&#259; în stare de de&#355;inere, de c&#259;tre\ninstan&#355;a corespunz&#259;toare în a c&#259;rei circumscrip&#355;ie se\nafl&#259; locul de de&#355;inere.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_10826369\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1114\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_10826369\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Hot&#259;rârea de înlocuire, r&#259;mas&#259;\ndefinitiv&#259;, se pune în executare potrivit dispozi&#355;iilor art. 555-557.</span></p>"}